imdb.plot outline: Nanthisa, the dashing girl of the company, she is the head of personal department and is the person whose should see other to follow the company's rules but she was the one who always break it. She come to work late everyday because hers house is away from the company and she has to wait for the permission from hers grandmother and mother before going to work. More over, the traffic and the cars that increase make her to come even more late which result in Phim commanding her to rent his condo or else he has to kick her out from the company. She has to do as his command and she get to meet Anggurt whose live next door to Phim's condo.
